com.interpss.core.aclf.hvdc
Interface HvdcLine2T

All Superinterfaces:
Branch, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
HvdcLine2TImpl
public interface HvdcLine2T
extends Branch

A representation of the model object 'Line2 T'. Always assume fromBus(rectifier) -> toBus(invetor)

The following features are supported:

  • Compond R
  • Control Mode
  • Meter End
  • Control Side
  • Power Demand
  • Scheduled DC Voltage
  • Rectifier
  • Inverter

See Also:
HvdcLinePackage.getHvdcLine2T()
